<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>403 Forbidden</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #2d3142;
            color: #f9f9f9;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 4em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .robot-img {
            width: 250px;
            height: auto;
            margin: 30px auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 5em;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .back-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 2px solid #f9f9f9;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #2d3142;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <img class="robot-img" src="/images/robot.png" alt="Error Robot">
    <h1 class="error-code">Credenciales Incorrectas</h1>
    <p>Oops! parece que tu correo electrónico o tu contraseña no coinciden.</p>
    <p>Nuestro amistoso guardia no puede dejarte pasar!</p>
    <a class="back-link" href="/">Volver</a>
</body>
</html>
